Description: Feature-rich screenshot application
 GScrot is a feature-rich screenshot program. 
 You can take a screenshot of a specific area, window, your whole screen, or even of a website - apply different effects to it, draw on it to highlight points, and then upload to a image hosting site, all within one window.
 .
 The GScrot homepage is http://launchpad.net/gscrot
